text: See also: Hengelo, Gelderland \---- Hengelo is a municipality in the province of Overijssel, the Netherlands. About 81,000 people were living there in 2021. It lies in Twente region. The University of Twente lies just across the municipal border in Enschede. == References == * Plaatsengids.nl Category:Cities in Overijssel Category:Municipalities of Overijssel Category:Twente
